description:
Searching for a fun family day out? The 2011 AA Days Out app features over 1,800 attractions across the country, from visitor centres, stately homes, castles and gardens, to theme parks, zoos, museums and galleries. 

  Entries may include a description, price info, telephone numbers, website addresses and more.  

The 2011 AA Days Out Guide app includes the following main features:   Over 1,800 attractions in England, Scotland and Wales  - fully installed content - price information - descriptions - including opening times - facilities  - telephone numbers - links to websites - search around your current location or select a location.
